<title>USA: Pilgrim America to convert to open-end fund.</title>
<headline>Pilgrim America to convert to open-end fund.</headline>
<dateline>PHOENIX 1997-08-06</dateline>
<text>
<p>Pilgrim America Bank and Thrift Fund Inc said it will convert from a closed-end investment company to an open-end investment company, pending shareholder approval.</p>
<p>The company said it will submit its proposal to shareholders to convert to an open-end investment company at a special meeting in October.</p>
</text>
